  <h1>Gitea Mirror Architecture</h1>
  
  <p>This document provides a comprehensive overview of the Gitea Mirror application architecture.</p>
  
  <h2>System Overview</h2>
  
  <p>Gitea Mirror is a web application that automates the mirroring of GitHub repositories to Gitea instances.</p>
  
  <p>The application is built using:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Astro</strong>: Web framework for the frontend</li>
    <li><strong>React</strong>: Component library for interactive UI elements</li>
    <li><strong>Shadcn UI</strong>: UI component library built on Tailwind CSS</li>
    <li><strong>SQLite</strong>: Database for storing configuration and state</li>
    <li><strong>Node.js</strong>: Runtime environment for the backend</li>
  </ul>
</main>
